{"tid":1535823,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"彭定康96年就已經知香港人寧願攬炒都唔願意做奴隸","createTime":"2019-09-03T13:27:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T14:32:08.000Z","uid":314892,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"e77d84dd75748bedcb0294845f9a1da3aa241afd","tid":1535823,"uid":314892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T13:27:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://library.legco.gov.hk:1443/search~S10?/Xm%3A(Policy%20Address)&amp;l=eng&amp;m=&amp;Da=1995&amp;Db=1997&amp;SORT=D&amp;searchscope=10&amp;b=lcdms/Xm%3A(Policy%20Address)&amp;l=eng&amp;m=&amp;Da=1995&amp;Db=1997&amp;SORT=D&amp;searchscope=10&amp;b=lcdms&amp;SUBKEY=m%3A(Policy+Address)/1%2C181%2C181%2CB/frameset&amp;FF=Xm%3A%28Policy+Address%29&amp;SORT=D&amp;3%2C3%2C\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Flibrary.legco.gov.hk%3A1443%2Fsearch~S10%3F%2FXm%253A%28Policy%2520Address%29%26l%3Deng%26m%3D%26Da%3D1995%26Db%3D1997%26SORT%3DD%26searchscope%3D10%26b%3Dlcdms%2FXm%253A%28Policy%2520Address%29%26l%3Deng%26m%3D%26Da%3D1995%26Db%3D1997%26SORT%3DD%26searchscope%3D10%26b%3Dlcdms%26SUBKEY%3Dm%253A%28Policy%2BAddress%29%2F1%252C181%252C181%252CB%2Fframeset%26FF%3DXm%253A%2528Policy%2BAddress%2529%26SORT%3DD%263%252C3%252C&d=wLht58ApaBOsBOdSjqbSDYlFrThteLnMWGuqQSPs63E%3D&h=27b5763b\" target=\"_blank\">https://library.legco.gov.hk:1443/search~S10?/Xm%3A(Policy%20Address)&amp;l=eng&amp;m=&amp;Da=1995&amp;Db=1997&amp;SORT=D&amp;searchscope=10&amp;b=lcdms/Xm%3A(Policy%20Address)&amp;l=eng&amp;m=&amp;Da=1995&amp;Db=1997&amp;SORT=D&amp;searchscope=10&amp;b=lcdms&amp;SUBKEY=m%3A(Policy+Address)/1%2C181%2C181%2CB/frameset&amp;FF=Xm%3A%28Policy+Address%29&amp;SORT=D&amp;3%2C3%2C</a><br />\n<br />\n1996年10月2日既施政報告<br />\n<br />\n除左最多人知果段 &quot;my anxiety is not that this community's autonomy would be usurped by Beijing, but that it could be given away bit by bit by some people in Hong Kong&quot; (&quot;我感到憂慮的，不是香港的自主權會被北京剝奪，而是這項權利會一點一滴地斷送在香港某些人手裏。&quot;) <br />\n<br />\n呢項不幸俾彭督講中左，但係其實彭督之後講既野好激勵我地香港人架<br />\nHong Kong, it seems to me, has always lived by the author, Jack LONDON's credo:<br />\n &quot;I would rather be ashes than dust,<br />\n I would rather my spark should burn out in a brilliant blaze,<br />\n Than it should be stifled in dry rot.<br />\n I would rather be a superb meteor,<br />\n With every atom of me in magnificent glow,<br />\n Than a sleepy and permanent planet.&quot;<br />\n<br />\n在我看來，香港一直在生活中實踐作家傑克‧倫敦(Jack LONDON)的信條：<br />\n &ldquo;寧化飛灰，不作浮塵。<br />\n &ldquo;寧投熊熊烈火，光盡而滅；<br />\n &ldquo;不伴寂寂朽木，默然同腐。<br />\n &ldquo;寧為耀目流星，迸發萬丈光芒；<br />\n &ldquo;不羨永恒星體，悠悠沉睡終古。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\nWhatever the challenges ahead, nothing, nothing should bring this meteor crashing to earth, nothing should snuff out its glow. I hope that Hong Kong will take tomorrow by storm. And when it does, history will stand and cheer.<br />\n<br />\n前路不管有何挑戰，都不會，我重複，都不會使這顆流星飛墜，光華從此消逝。我深願香港能奮然而起，征服未來，那時候，歷史也必為之動容，起立喝采。<br />\n<br />\n希望呢番説話鼓勵到大家"},{"pid":"c9b021a44ed6651ab7ff68348b409c6f4e394941","tid":1535823,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T13:27:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bf48f16e522fc6b041f78962ed990d6d9240b7c3","tid":1535823,"uid":290815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T13:27:56.000Z","msg":"其實要突破困局，依家只有「__」依個選項！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1534823\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1534823</a><br />\n<br />\n延伸閱讀：<br />\n香港民權抗爭&mdash;&mdash;五大訴求，缺一不可？我們需要更多！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1530124\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1530124</a>"},{"pid":"0dbcad681fe5f01edbf59d899ba28803d851ea96","tid":1535823,"uid":279236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T13:28:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76e9eb520733e56557ef31398